text: Mars () is a rural locality (a village) in Gorkovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 78 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Kushnarenkovo, 8 km from Ilikovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Mars, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
